text: Lachenalia nordenstamii is a species of plant in the family Asparagaceae. The name is accepted by some authorities, but not by the World Checklist of Selected Plant Families. It is endemic to Namibia. Its natural habitat is rocky areas. ==References== * Category:Flora of Namibia nordenstamii Category:Least concern plants Category:Taxonomy articles created by Polbot
